#: ml-slider.php:2117
msgid ""
"YouTube slides will display your videos with auto play, mute, lazy load, "
"the ability to hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"YouTube-dias viser dine videoer med automatisk afspilning, lydløs, lazy "
"load, mulighed for at skjule kontroller og meget mere."

#: ml-slider.php:2150
msgid "Create slideshows with your posts"
msgstr "Opret diasshows med dine indlæg"

#: ml-slider.php:2154
msgid ""
"With Post Feed slides, you can build slideshows with your latest posts, "
"events, or WooCommerce products."
msgstr ""
"Med Post Feed-dias kan du bygge diasshows med dine seneste indlæg, "
"begivenheder eller WooCommerce-produkter."

#: ml-slider.php:2158
msgid ""
"Post Feed slides will automatically display your posts with images, text, "
"custom fields, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Post Feed-dias viser automatisk dine indlæg med billeder, tekst, "
"brugerdefinerede felter og meget mere."

#: ml-slider.php:2193
msgid "Create slideshows with images stored outside of WordPress"
msgstr "Opret diasshows med billeder gemt uden for WordPress"

#: ml-slider.php:2197
msgid ""
"With External URL slides, you can load images directly from non-WordPress "
"sources such as CDNs or image hosts."
msgstr ""
"Med Ekstern URL-dias kan du indlæse billeder direkte fra "
"ikke-WordPress-kilder som CDN'er eller billedværter."

#: ml-slider.php:2201
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"External URL slides give you all the power of MetaSlider Slideshow, using "
"images stored anywhere you want."
msgstr ""
"Ekstern URL-dias giver dig al kraften fra MetaSlider, ved at bruge billeder "
"gemt hvor som helst du ønsker."

#: ml-slider.php:2236
msgid "Create slideshows with videos in your media library"
msgstr "Opret diasshows med videoer i dit mediebibliotek"

#: ml-slider.php:2240
msgid ""
"With Local Video slides, you can build beautiful slideshows with videos in "
"your WordPress media library."
msgstr ""
"Med Lokale Video-dias kan du bygge smukke diasshows med videoer i dit "
"WordPress-mediebibliotek."

#: ml-slider.php:2244
msgid ""
"Local Video slides will display your MP4, WebM, and MOV videos with cover "
"images, auto play, mute, lazy load, the ability to hide controls, and much "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Lokale video slides vil vise dine MP4, WebM og MOV videoer med "
"coverbilleder, automatisk afspilning, lydløst, lazy load, muligheden for at "
"skjule kontroller og meget mere."

#: ml-slider.php:2279
msgid "Create slideshows with videos stored outside of WordPress"
msgstr "Opret diasshows med videoer gemt uden for WordPress"

#: ml-slider.php:2283
msgid ""
"With External Video slides, you can add videos directly from non-WordPress "
"sources."
msgstr ""
"Med ekstern video slides kan du tilføje videoer direkte fra ikke-WordPress "
"kilder."

#: ml-slider.php:2287
msgid ""
"External Video Slides will display your MP4, WebM, and MOV videos. Features "
"include text captions, cover images, auto play, mute, lazy load, the "
"ability to hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Eksterne video slides vil vise dine MP4, WebM og MOV videoer. Funktioner "
"inkluderer tekstundertekster, coverbilleder, automatisk afspilning, "
"lydløst, lazy load, muligheden for at skjule kontroller og meget mere."

#: ml-slider.php:2322
msgid "Create slideshows with custom HTML"
msgstr "Opret diasshows med brugerdefineret HTML"

#: ml-slider.php:2326
msgid ""
"With Custom HTML slides, you can design slides using images, HTML and CSS. "
"This gives you complete control over the layout and styling."
msgstr ""
"Med brugerdefinerede HTML slides kan du designe slides ved hjælp af "
"billeder, HTML og CSS. Dette giver dig fuld kontrol over layout og styling."

#: ml-slider.php:2361
msgid "Create slideshows with Tiktok Videos"
msgstr "Opret diasshows med TikTok-videoer"

#: ml-slider.php:2365
