msgstr "Denne slide-type viser billeder fra mapper i dit WordPress Mediebibliotek."

#: ml-slider.php:2463
msgid "Create slideshows with Post Images"
msgstr "Opret diasshows med postbilleder"

#: ml-slider.php:2467
msgid ""
"The Post Images slide type extracts images from the current post and "
"displays them as slides."
msgstr ""
"Postbilleder slide-typen udtrækker billeder fra det aktuelle indlæg og "
"viser dem som slides."

#: ml-slider.php:2471
msgid ""
"This slide type supports featured images, post content images, WooCommerce "
